            <li><a class="external" href="https://www.webmd.com/cancer/pancreatic-cancer/information-pancreatic-cancer" target="_blank" rel="noopener ">WebMd - Pancreatic Cancer Health Center</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

    </div>
				</div>
			</div>

    	







































